{"name":"Ether Flask","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-corked-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nosUAidVyWaTwFwB"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This enchanted draught concentrates the ambient mist within the user's body and clears the mind, enabling an exhausted mage to continue casting spells.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>On use: recover 2d4+10 Focus.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031101709,"modifiedTime":1776031101709,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"oTw6hqyheq2BjdJt"}
{"name":"Regeneration Draught","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-capped-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nk0e59WkVjwiUb5g"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>Consumable, 1 Minor action</p>\n<p>This enchanted draught causes the wounded flesh to knit together and allows one to persevere in combat where otherwise wounds might have proven too great. This version lasts longer in exchange for a less concentrated acute effect.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>On use: recover 2d4+4 Health for 3 rounds.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031103693,"modifiedTime":1776031103693,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"07mp5W5m9hXYwAX9"}
{"name":"Revitalization Charge","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-tube-corked-glowing-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fzK2MSTtGZhM2Uzn"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p>This mysterious substance can recall the soul of a fallen Immortal into their physical form instantaneously, provided that said form has not yet discorporated. It is used by pouring over the fallen body, whereupon it swiftly evaporates, briefly leaving a sickly red glow.</p>\n<p>Inquiry into the origins and the manufacture of Revitalization Charges is strongly discouraged by the factions. There may be a deeper secret to it ...</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>Target: 1 dead immortal within 5 squares.</p>\n<p>On use: the target immediately revives with full health and focus. They retain their place within the initiative order and can act as normal on their turn.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031105501,"modifiedTime":1776031105501,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"V84KjvhBaHuu6g1h"}
{"name":"Potent Ether Flask","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-jar-corked-glowing-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1eLhKXTRNA1aQol6"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This enchanted draught concentrates the ambient mist within the user's body and clears the mind, enabling an exhausted mage to continue casting spells.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>On use: recover 2d6+18 Focus.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031107768,"modifiedTime":1776031107768,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"qumS54m6mp2tCl0m"}
{"name":"Potent Regeneration Draught","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-capped-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.H256eTC2K7JA5BBT"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>Consumable, 1 Minor action</p>\n<p>This enchanted draught causes the wounded flesh to knit together and allows one to persevere in combat where otherwise wounds might have proven too great. This version lasts longer in exchange for a less concentrated acute effect.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>On use: recover 2d6+8 Health for 3 rounds.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031110140,"modifiedTime":1776031110140,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"EL5Ut4t2bXOesdcj"}
