{"name":"Prima Materia, Vial","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hHhFwiitkahicqiO"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p>The substance contained within this bottle seems to glow with an inner light and power. It feels preternaturally heavy in the hand.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031137519,"modifiedTime":1776031137519,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"8kG5bR7z1HdXQrpJ"}
{"name":"Materia Nigra, Vial","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-labeled-medicine-capped-red-black.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.X2EeYRY5V7TMIBq8"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p>A corrupted form of Prima Materia, the stuff of creation itself. Ingredient of some Legendary Rituals. If used for lesser rituals, this substance corrupts their effects -- useful, if used with care.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1775946600658,"modifiedTime":1776031140156,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Otu7ae52lY5auPGQ"}
{"name":"Materia Rubrior, Vial","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-bulb-corked-glowing-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.X2EeYRY5V7TMIBq8"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p>The fully realized form of Prima Materia, the stuff of creation itself. Ingredient of some Legendary Rituals. If used for lesser rituals, this substance is worth 20 Magnitude.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":null,"charge":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1775946600658,"modifiedTime":1776031141936,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Xj4uozhioaww0lUD"}
{"name":"Red Healing Potion","type":"useItem","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-corked-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6PZrHqx0V0Bk7ww2"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This magical draught unnaturally quickens the body's healing process, allowing a lightly wounded soldier to recover from his injuries within minutes upon ingestion. Overuse is not recommended, as each use carries a chance of overshooting its goal and provoking uncontrolled tissue growth.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>On use: recover 1d6+6 Hit Points.</p>","damageType":"crushing","range":0,"effects":"","class":"","quantity":null,"bulk":0.25,"charge":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1776031146673,"modifiedTime":1776031146673,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"sbBaU9cAtFh6wq9r"}
